indentication division.
program-id palindrome.
data division.

working-storage section.
01 sre1 pic a(10) value 'HELLOCOBOL'.
01 STR2 PIC A(10).
01 I PIC 9(2) VALUE 10.
01 J PIC 9(2) VALUE 01.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
   PERFORM PARA1 UNTIL J>10
   DISPLAY STR1.
   DISPLAY STR2.
   STOP RUN.
PARA1.
   MOVE STR1(I:1) TO STR2(J:1).
   ADD 1 TO J.
